## API Error Handling
```typescript
try {
  await employeesApi.create(formData);
  navigate('/employees');
} catch (error) {
  if (error instanceof ApiError) {
    if (error.details) {
      // Field-level errors
      setErrors(error.details);
    } else {
      // General error
      setError(error.message);
    }
  }
}
```
